  <summary>The Open Thesaurus</summary>
  <url type="homepage">https://artha.sourceforge.net</url>
  <description>
    <p>
      Artha is a handy off-line thesaurus based on WordNet with distinct features like global hotkey look-up, passive desktop notifications, regular expression based search, etc.. Artha may be used as a free open-source replacement to the proprietary WordWeb Pro.
    </p>
    <p>GNOME Shell: Install the "AppIndicator and KStatusNotifierItem Support" extension from the Extensions Manager, or the tray icon and application window will not be visible.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Hotkey look-up from inside any window</li>
      <li>Passive notifications for seamless workflow</li>
      <li>Spelling suggestions for a misspelled word</li>
      <li>Powerful regular expressions based search</li>
      <li>Volume and speed adjustment</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
